Privacy policy

General

Advanced Flashlight is developed by BullPresents, with a few people helping from time to time, mostly with translations.

Privacy Policy ("Policy") describes how information obtained from users is collected, used and disclosed.

By using Advanced Flashlight, you agree that your personal information will be handled as described in this Policy.

Information being collected

Simple Gallery does not collect any personal identifiable information.

The `android.permission.CAMERA` permission uses for camera light to turn on or off

Changes to the Policy

If the Policy changes, the modification date below will be updated. The Policy may change from time to time, so please be sure to check back periodically.

Last modified: 10 February, 2019.

Contact

